
# 📊 Customer Churn Prediction System

This project builds an end-to-end machine learning system to predict customer churn using tabular business data.  
It compares a baseline model with an advanced tree-based model and explains predictions using permutation importance.

The goal is to help businesses identify high-risk customers and design effective retention strategies.

---

## 🚀 Project Objectives

- Handle both numerical and categorical features
- Build a baseline Logistic Regression model
- Train an improved Random Forest model
- Evaluate performance using F1-score
- Explain predictions using permutation importance
- Generate business-friendly reports

