## 📊 Dataset

A synthetic telecom customer dataset is generated with realistic patterns.

### Features

| Feature Name       | Type        | Description                          |
|--------------------|-------------|--------------------------------------|
| tenure_months      | Numerical   | Months customer stayed               |
| monthly_charges    | Numerical   | Monthly billing amount               |
| contract_type      | Categorical | Contract duration type               |
| internet_service   | Categorical | Type of internet service             |
| payment_method     | Categorical | Customer payment method              |

### Target Variable

| Column | Meaning              |
|--------|----------------------|
| churn  | 1 = Left, 0 = Stayed |

Churn probabilities are generated based on:
- Contract type
- Monthly charges
- Customer tenure

This makes the dataset realistic and suitable for modeling.

