## ⚙️ Machine Learning Pipeline

The system uses Scikit-learn Pipelines to ensure clean and reproducible workflows.

### Preprocessing

- Numerical Features → StandardScaler
- Categorical Features → OneHotEncoder
- Combined using ColumnTransformer

### Models

1. Logistic Regression (Baseline)
2. Random Forest Classifier (Improved Model)

### Evaluation Metric

- F1-score (chosen due to class imbalance in churn data)

---

## 📈 Model Training

The dataset is split into:

- 80% Training
- 20% Testing

Stratified sampling is used to preserve churn ratio.

Both models are trained using the same preprocessing pipeline.

